        <h4 class="text-center my-5">Truth Table Generator</h4>
        <div class="row project-description mb-5">
          <div class="col-lg-6 offset-lg-1 project-picture ttg">
            <img src="https://res.cloudinary.com/dklkew1yh/image/upload/v1619405908/portfolio/ttg_hsw9vn.png" alt="example truth table" class="img-fluid"/>
          </div>
          <div class="col-lg-4 description-container">
            <p class="mt-3">
              A Node module which creates a truth table from an array of strings representing statements of propositional logic.
              Utilizes recursive descent parsing to read and organize inputs.  Includes an extensive test file (found
              in the 'development' branch on github).  Mocha is used for the tests, and the rest was done from scratch.
            </p>
            <div class="project-links">
              <a href="https://www.npmjs.com/package/generate-truth-table">View on NPM</a> <br>
              <a href="/generateTruthTable">Browser implementation</a><br>
              <a href="https://github.com/masimoncic/generate-truth-table">Github repository</a>

            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
